#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; is a simple image scanning application that does nothing more "
"than scan and save images. &skanlite; can open a save dialog for every image "
"scanned or save the images immediately in a specified folder with auto-"
"generated names and format. The user can also choose to show the scanned "
"image before saving."
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; je jednostavna aplikacija za skeniranje fotogafija koja ne radi "
"ništa osim skeniranja i spremanja. &skanlite; može otvoriti okvir za "
"spremanje svake fotografije skenirane ili spremiti fotografiju direktno u "
"folder sa auto generisanjem imena i formata. Korisnik također može odabrati "
"prikaz skenirane fotografije prije spremanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&skanlite; can save images in all the formats supported by KDE. For "
#| "example the following formats:"
msgid ""
"&skanlite; can save images in all the formats supported by &Qt;. For example "
"the following formats:"
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; može spremiti fotografije svih formata podržanih od KDE. Na "
"primjer slijedeće formate:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "png (8 and 16 bits per color)"
msgstr "png (8 i 16 bita po boji)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "jpeg, jpg, jpeg 2000"
msgstr "jpeg, jpg, jpeg 2000"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>bmp</para>"
msgstr "<para>bmp</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can check the status of your scanner support from the SANE project "
#| "website by entering the information on this search page: <ulink url="
#| "\"http://www.sane-project.org/cgi-bin/driver.pl\">http://www.sane-project."
#| "org/cgi-bin/driver.pl</ulink>."
msgid ""
"You can check the status of your scanner support from the SANE project "
"website through the <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/sane-supported-"
"devices.html\">Supported Devices page on the SANE website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Možete provjeriti status vašeg skenera podržanog od strane SANE projekat "
"internet stranice unošenjem informacija na ovoj stranici za pretraživanje: "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/cgi-bin/driver.pl\">http://www.sane-"
"project.org/cgi-bin/driver.pl</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &skanlite;"
msgstr "Korištenje &skanlite;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanner Selection"
msgstr "Izbor skenera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A default scanner can be specified on the command line of &skanlite; using "
"<userinput>skanlite -d [device name]</userinput> in a terminal. If the "
"selected scanner cannot be opened or if no default scanner is provided, a "
"scanner selection dialog is opened."
msgstr ""
"Zadani skener može biti specificiran u komandnoj liniji &skanlite;  "
"korištenjem <userinput>skanlite -d [device name]</userinput> u terminalu. "
"Ako odabrani skener ne može biti otvoren ili ako nema zadanog skenera, "
"otvara se okvir za odabir skenera."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&skanlite; scanner selection dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&skanlite; okvir za izbor skenera</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&skanlite; scanner selection dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&skanlite; okvir za izbor skenera</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can choose the scanner to be used and press <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> to open the scanner. Pressing <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> will "
"cause &skanlite; to exit."
msgstr ""
"Korisnik može odabrati skener pritiskom  <guibutton>OK</guibutton>  da "
"otvorite skener. Pritiskanje <guibutton>Poništi</guibutton> zatvara  "
"&skanlite;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>No scanner found</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nije pronađen nijedan skener</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>No scanner found</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nije pronađen nijedan skener</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case no devices were found, maybe because the scanner is not plugged in "
"or switched off, correct that. Then the <guibutton>Reload device list</"
"guibutton> can be used to reload the list of scanners."
msgstr ""
"Ako nije pronađen nijedan uređaj, jer skener nije priključen ili upaljen, "
"popravite to. Onda možete koristiti <guibutton>Ponovo učitaj listu uređaja</"
"guibutton> za ponovno učitavanje liste skenera."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all drivers/backends support this feature. In that case quit &skanlite;, "
"connect your scanner and restart the application."
msgstr ""
"Ne podržavaju svi drajveri/podrške ovaj dodatak. U tom slučaju ugasite "
"&skanlite;, priključite skener i ponovo pokrenite aplikaciju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; Main Window"
msgstr "&skanlite; Glavni prozor"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&skanlite; main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&skanlite; glavni prozor</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&skanlite; main window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&skanlite; glavni prozor</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the main window, the user has two sets of scan options: <guilabel>Basic "
"Options</guilabel> and <guilabel>Scanner Specific Options</guilabel>. The "
"<guilabel>Basic Options</guilabel> tab contains the most common parameters "
"that the SANE scanner backends provide, while the <guilabel>Scanner Specific "
"Options</guilabel> tab contains all the options of the backend. The options "
"listed here depend on SANE support for your driver: libksane (which "
"&skanlite; uses) should be able to display most of the types of parameters "
"that SANE provides (analog gamma tables are not supported at this time)."
msgstr ""
"U glavnom prozoru  korisnik može podesiti dvije vrste opcija skeniranja: "
"<guilabel>Osnovne opcije</guilabel> i <guilabel>Posebne opcije skenera</"
"guilabel>. <guilabel>Osnovne opcije</guilabel> kartica sadrži većinu "
"parametara koje SANE skener omogućava, dok <guilabel>Posebne opcije skenera</"
"guilabel>  kartica sadrži sve ostale opcije. Ove opcije zavise od SANE "
"podrške za drajver: libksane (koje &skanlite; koristi ) bi trebao biti u "
"mogućnosti da prikaže većinu tipova parametara koje SANE omogućava(analogne "
"gama tabele nisu podržane trenutno)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Scanner Specific Options tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kartica sa posebnim opcijama skenera</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scanner Specific Options tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kartica sa posebnim opcijama skenera</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scanner specific options contains more detailed options of the backends. "
"&skanlite; (libksane) does not have any special handling for these options."
msgstr ""
"Specifične opcije skenera sadrže detaljnije opcije za podršku.  &skanlite; "
"(libksane) nema nekih posebnih alata za ove opcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with your settings, you can use the little arrow on the "
"top of the options splitter. When clicked it collapses or expands the "
"options. The collapser can overlap the preview area, but fades away when the "
"mouse cursor moves out of the collapser."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste zadovoljni vašim postavkama, možete korisiti malu strelicu na vrhu "
"djeljitelja opcija. Kada je kliknete skuplja ili proširuje opcije. Širenje "
"može pokriti područje prikaza, ali nestaje čim je kursor miša pomjeren sa "
"strelice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanning"
msgstr "Skeniranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To scan an image, the user can start with a preview scan and then select the "
"part of the scan area to do the final scan on. The preview scan is started "
"by pressing the preview button."
msgstr ""
"Da skenira fotografiju, korisnik može početi od prikaza skeniranja i "
"odaberite područje skeniranja u krajnjem skeniranju. Prikaz skeniranja se "
"dobije pritiskom prikaz tipke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Preview Button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Tipka za prikaz</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Preview Button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tipka za prikaz</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the preview is scanned the area for the final image can be selected."
msgstr "Kada je prikaz skeniran dio za krajnju sliku može biti odabran."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Selection and zoom</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Odabir i povećavanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Selection and zoom</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Odabir i povećavanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To better select the image the user can zoom in, out, to the current "
"selection or zoom to fit the whole preview to the window."
msgstr ""
"Za bolji odabir slike korisnik može koristiti povećavanje, smanjivanje "
"trenutnog dijela slike ili povećavanje da stane cijelog prozora za prikaz."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The \"zoom to fit\" button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>\"Povećaj da stane\" tipka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The \"zoom to fit\" button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase> \"Povećaj da stane\" tipka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the image is selected the final image can be acquired by pressing the "
"final scan button."
msgstr ""
"Kada je odabrana fotografija krajnja fotografija može biti stvorena "
"pritiskom na tipku za krajnji odabit."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The final scan button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Tipka za krajnji odabir</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The final scan button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tipka za krajnji odabir</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "You will see the progress of the scan."
msgstr "Vidjećete napredak skeniranja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Scanning in progress</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skeniranje u toku</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scanning in progress</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skeiranje u toku</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If <guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> is selected in the "
#| "settings, the scanned image is displayed in a preview window as you can "
#| "see below on the screenshot. If <guibutton>Save</guibutton> is pressed, "
#| "the image is saved and if <guibutton>Close</guibutton> is pressed the "
#| "preview is discarded and you return to the main window."
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> is selected in the settings, "
"the scanned image is displayed in a preview window as you can see below on "
"the screenshot. If <guibutton>Save</guibutton> is pressed, the image is "
"saved and if <guibutton>Discard</guibutton> is pressed the preview is "
"discarded and you return to the main window."
msgstr ""
"Ako je <guilabel>Pregled prije spremanja</guilabel> odabran u postavkama, "
"skenirana fotografija je prikazana u prozoru za pregled  kao što vidite u "
"snimci ekrana ispod. Ako je <guibutton>Spremi</guibutton> tipka pritisnuta, "
"fotografija je spremljena i ako je <guibutton>Zatvori</guibutton> tipka "
"pritisnuta pregled se odbacuje i vraćeni ste u glavni prozor."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Preview Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Prozor za pregled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Preview Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prozor za pregled</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanning Multiple Selections"
msgstr "Skeniranje višestrukih dijelova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you need only certain parts of an image. Instead of scanning the "
"whole picture and then using a graphics application (&eg; &kolourpaint;) to "
"save the different image parts into separate files, use &skanlite;'s "
"multiple selection feature."
msgstr ""
"Ponekad trebate samo određene dijelove fotografije. Umjesto skeniranja "
"cijele fotografije i korištenja grafičke aplikacije (&eg; &kolourpaint;) za "
"spremanje dijelova fotografije u različite okumente, koristite &skanlite;-ov "
"dodatak za višestruko odabiranje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Multiple Selections</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Višestruki odabir</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Multiple Selections</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Višestruki odabir</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scan a preview and then use the &LMB; to select the first part of the image "
"in the preview. Hover the selected area with mouse cursor and click on the "
"green <guiicon>+</guiicon> icon to select the area. Selected areas are "
"indicated by a red border. Now select the next parts of the image in the "
"same way."
msgstr ""
"Skenirajte pregled i koristite &LMB; da odaberete prvi dio fotografije u "
"pregledu. Pokrite odabrano područje sa pokazivačem miša i pritisnite zelenu  "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon> ikonu da odaberete područje. Odabrana područja su "
"označena crvenim okvirom. Sada odaberite slijedeće dijelove fotografije na "
"isti način."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a single selection hover the area with the mouse cursor and click "
"on the red <guiicon>-</guiicon> icon. With <guilabel>Clear Selections</"
"guilabel> from the context menu launched with the &RMB; all selections in a "
"preview can be removed."
msgstr ""
"Da odznačite neki dio fotografje pređite područje pokazivačem miša i "
"pritisnite <guiicon>-</guiicon> ikonu. Sa <guilabel>Poništi odabire</"
"guilabel> iz kontekst menija pokrenutog sa &RMB; svi odabiri u pregledu mogu "
"biti uklonjeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you placed two separate images or photos on you scanner and started a "
"preview &skanlite; automatically preselect the different areas. This "
"behaviour can be switched off in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ako stavite dvije odvojene fotografije ili slike na vaš skener i pokrenete "
"pregled &skanlite; automatski odabere druga područja. Ovo ponašanje može "
"biti isključeno u okviru sa postavkama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with your choice starting the final batch scan of all "
"selections. The images are saved using the batch renaming feature described "
"in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste zadovoljni vašim izborom počnite završni dio skeniranja svih "
"područja. Fotografije su spremljene korištenjem dodatka za preimenovanje "
"opisanog u ovom dijelu okvira sa postavkama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; settings"
msgstr "&skanlite; postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking the <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> button, the settings dialog "
"is brought up before the main window. You can choose the most important "
"settings here."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom <guibutton>Postavke</guibutton> tipke, okvir sa postavkama se "
"prikazuje ispred glavnog prozora. Ovdje možete odabrati najznačajnije "
"postavke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &skanlite; settings dialog"
msgstr "Ovdje je snimak ekrana &skanlite; okvira sa postavkama"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; settings dialog"
msgstr "&skanlite; okvir sa postavkama"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview before saving:"
msgstr "Pregled prije spremanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can chose to preview the image before saving. In this case the "
"<guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> option can be left checked. If "
"the user does not want to preview the image this option should then be "
"unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Korisnik može odabrati da pregleda fotografije prije spremanja. U ovom "
"slučaju <guilabel>Pregled prije spremanja</guilabel> opcija može biti "
"označena. Ako korisnik ne želi pregled fotografije prije spremanja onda "
"opciju treba odznačiti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Mode:"
msgstr "Mod za spremanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting allows you to choose how &skanlite; will save the images. If "
"you choose <guilabel>Open the save dialog for every image</guilabel> the "
"save dialog will be opened for every scanned image. If you prefer &skanlite; "
"to auto-save (by auto-generating a name and saving the image in a predefined "
"folder) you can choose <guilabel>Open the save dialog for the first image "
"only</guilabel>. This option will open the following \"Save Location\" "
"dialog for the first scanned image."
msgstr ""
"Ova postavka omogućava odabir načina spremanja fotografija u  &skanlite;. "
"Ako odaberete <guilabel>Otvori okvir za spremanje za svaku fotograafiju</"
"guilabel> okvir za spremanje će biti otvoren za svaku skeniranu fotografiju. "
"Ako preferirate &scanlite; auto spremanje (automatsko generisanje imena i "
"spremanje fotografije u određeni folder) možete odabrati <guilabel>Otvori "
"okvir za spremanje samo za prvu fotografiju</guilabel>. Ova opcija če "
"otvoriti slijedeći \"Lokacija za spremanje\" okvir za prvu skeniranu "
"fotografiju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &skanlite; save location dialog"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana &skanlite; okvira lokacije za spremanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; Save Location dialog."
msgstr "&skanlite; Okvir lokacije za spremanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Location:"
msgstr "Lokacija za spremanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines the default save location and file naming. The default "
"save location is your home folder and you can change this location by "
"clicking on the <guibutton>...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija definira zadane lokacije za spremanje i imenovanje dokumenata. "
"Zadana lokacija je u vašem osnovnom folderu i možete je promijeniti "
"pritiskom na <guibutton>...</guibutton> tipku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name Format:"
msgstr "Format imena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This parameter defines the image prefix for the auto-saved images and is "
"also the suggested name for the image in the save dialog. The auto-saved "
"image will have a numeric suffix (the ### will be replaced by numbers) that "
"is increased every time an image is saved."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj parametar definira prefiks za automatsko spremanje fotografija i "
"predlaže ime za fotografiju u okviru za spremanje. Automatski spremljena "
"fotografija će imati brojni sufiks (### će biti zamjenjeno brojevima) koji "
"se povećava svaki put kad je fotografija spremljena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can also choose the save format of the file, default is png."
msgstr "Možete odabrati format za spremanje dokumenta, zadani je png."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify save quality:"
msgstr "Specificiraj kvalitet spremanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can chose to specify the image quality to be used for saving the "
"images. The image quality setting affects the compression level used for "
"saving. If <guilabel>Specify save quality</guilabel> is not checked, the "
"quality is the default value chosen by &Qt;."
msgstr ""
"Korisnik može odabrati kvalitet slike koji će biti korišten za spremanje. "
"Postavka kvaliteta utječe na nivo kompresije korišten za spremanje. Ako "
"<guilabel>Odaberi kvalitet spremanja</guilabel> polje nije označeno, "
"kvaliteta je zadano odabrana od strane &Qt;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set preview resolution (DPI)"
msgstr "Postavi rezoluciju pregleda (DPI)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; is using heuristics to try to get a sane resolution, but if that "
"fails and the resolution is too high or low, then the preview resolution can "
"be manually set with this option."
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; koristi heuristiku da dobije normalnu rezoluciju, ali ako to ne "
"uspije rezolucija je prevelika ili premala, onda se rezolucija pregleda može "
"ručno podesiti korištenjem ove opcije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable automatic selections"
msgstr "Onemogući automatske odabire"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default automatic selections are enabled; and after a preview, libksane "
"does try to automatically select the images in the preview and should batch "
"scan the selected areas. &eg; if you place two photos on the scanner and do "
"a preview, &skanlite; will automatically add selections of the photos."
msgstr ""
"Zadano automatski odabir je omogućen; i nakon pregleda, libskane pokušava "
"automatski odabrati fotografije i označiti odabrana područja. &eg; ako "
"postavite dvije fotografije na skener i odaberete pregled, &skanlite; će "
"automatski dodati odabrana područja fotografija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If on the other hand you are usually scanning documents it might be that the "
"automatic selection will select a lot of different parts in the documents "
"and you have to manually remove the selections. To avoid that tick the "
"checkbox and disable automatic selection."
msgstr ""
"S druge strane ako obično skenirate dokumente može se desiti da automatski "
"odabir odabere dosta različitih dijelova u dokumentu i morate ručno ukloniti "
"te oznake. Da izbjegnete to odznačite i onemogućite automatski odabir."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Revert scanner options to default values"
msgstr "Vrati opcije skenera na podrazumijevane vrijednosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last used settings are reloaded on startup. If you have screwed up the "
"options (for example if you have changed the color correction settings, "
"available in some backends, without knowing what they mean), the image can "
"start to look very odd. For that scenario this option provides a way to "
"revert the setting to the default values, which are a combination of backend "
"and libksane defaults."
msgstr ""
"Posljedne korištene opcije se ponovo učitaju na početku. Ako ste uprskali "
"opcije(na primjer ako ste promijenili postavke korekcije boje, dostupne za "
"podršku, bez poznavanja njihovog značenja), slika može izgledati jako čudno. "
"Za takav scenario ova opcija omogućava da se postavke vrate na zadane "
"vrijednosti, koje su kombinacija podrške i libskane zadanih vrijednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help, About, Settings and Close"
msgstr "Pomoć, O, Postavke i Zatvori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the main window you find the <guibutton>Help</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>About</guibutton>, <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> buttons."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu glavnog prozora imate <guibutton>Pomoć</guibutton>, <guibutton>O</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Postavke</guibutton> i <guibutton>Zatvori</guibutton> "
"tipke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Main Window Buttons</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Tipke u glavnom prozoru</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Main Window Buttons</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tipke u glavnom prozoru</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Help</guibutton> button brings up the &kde; Help center with "
"the &skanlite; manual. The <guibutton>About</guibutton> button brings up the "
"&kde; About dialog for &skanlite;. The <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> "
"button displays the settings dialog and the <guibutton>Close</guibutton> "
"button is used to exit &skanlite;."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Pomoć</guibutton> tipka pokreće &kde; Centar za pomoć unutar "
"&skanlite; uputstva.  <guibutton>O</guibutton> tipka pokreće &kde; O okvir "
"unutar &skanlite;. <guibutton>Postavke</guibutton> tipka prikazuje okvir sa "
"postavkama i <guibutton>Zatvori</guibutton> tipka se koristi za izlaz iz "
"&skanlite;."

